two years ago, not last week.

1095
01:19:25,788 --> 01:19:27,585
You people are derivative.

1096
01:19:27,656 --> 01:19:30,750
You're not viewing
a representation of hell.

1097
01:19:30,826 --> 01:19:31,758
You are hell.

1098
01:19:31,827 --> 01:19:36,161
You haven't produced
a real artist in over a decade.

1099
01:19:42,037 --> 01:19:44,335
...Screw this play...

1100
01:19:44,406 --> 01:19:47,500
and screw you people.

1101
01:20:15,137 --> 01:20:19,164
