a weekend lasted two days.

1102
01:20:19,241 --> 01:20:20,173
Am l wrong?

1103
01:20:20,242 --> 01:20:22,107
Did we switch
to a French workweek

1104
01:20:22,177 --> 01:20:23,439
while l wasn't looking?

1105
01:20:23,512 --> 01:20:24,740
Oh, look who's jealous.

1106
01:20:24,813 --> 01:20:25,905
ls there electricity

1107
