but when do they want you
to show up at McKinsey?

1110
01:20:32,254 --> 01:20:33,278
l'm not sure.

1111
01:20:33,355 --> 01:20:34,322
Absolutely not.

1112
01:20:34,390 --> 01:20:36,551
What do you mean
you're not sure?

1113
01:20:36,625 --> 01:20:38,058
l mean l don't know.

1114
01:20:38,127 --> 01:20:39,287
l haven't heard.

1115
01:20:43,298 --> 01:20:46,267
Okay, uh, listen.

1116
01:20:46,335 --> 01:20:50,237
Don't flip out but l'm thinking
of deferring it for a year.

1117
01:20:50,305 --> 01:20:51,329
What?

1118
01:20:51,407 --> 01:20:53,341
lt's only a year.

1119
01:20:53,409 --> 01:20:55,400
l'm burned out.
l'm tired.

1120
01:20:55,477 --> 01:20:57,672
What's this cop done to you?

1121
01:20:57,746 --> 01:21:02,149
He hasn't done anything.

1122
01:21:02,217 --> 01:21:05,277
Well...
maybe a little something.

1123
01:21:05,354 --> 01:21:08,812
He doesn't even know
this is what l'm thinking.

1124
01:21:08,891 --> 01:21:10,085
l think go with him.

1125
01:21:10,159 --> 01:21:12,821
So what if it takes up
a year of your life?

1126
01:21:12,895 --> 01:21:14,362
l mean, God, everybody thinks

1127
01:21:14,430 --> 01:21:16,455
that everything has
to be so planned out

1128
01:21:16,532 --> 01:21:18,363
you know, like our life is
on a rail

1129
01:21:18,434 --> 01:21:20,163
and one misstep,
it all goes away.

1130
01:21:20,235 --> 01:21:23,500
Basically...

1131
01:21:23,572 --> 01:21:26,507
who knows?

1132
01:21:26,575 --> 01:21:30,170
The last time you were this
irrational was with Embry.

1133
01:21:30,245 --> 01:21:33,078
Maybe that was the last time
l was happy.

1134
01:23:00,068 --> 01:23:02,628
Well, so l just said,
''The hell with it.''

1135
01:23:02,704 --> 01:23:04,831
Then l went
and climbed a mountain

1136
01:23:04,907 --> 01:23:06,898
but l didn't bring enough water.

1137
01:23:07,042 --> 01:23:08,907
So l got
a little disorientated

1138
01:23:09,044 --> 01:23:12,104
and the state police had to come
and pick me up.

1139
01:23:12,181 --> 01:23:16,880
lt was really more embarrassing
than anything else.

1140
01:23:16,952 --> 01:23:18,283
Oh, um...

1141
01:23:18,353 --> 01:23:21,481
Whatever happened
with that cop, right?

1142
01:23:21,557 --> 01:23:24,924
'Cause he was
kind of sweet on you, or...?

1143
01:23:25,060 --> 01:23:27,051
Um... l don't know.

1144
01:23:27,129 --> 01:23:30,257
l think he's in New Hampshire.

1145
01:23:30,332 --> 01:23:32,391
Oh.

1146
01:23:32,467 --> 01:23:35,231
Well, New Hampshire's nice
this time of year.

1147
01:23:35,304 --> 01:23:37,772
l've changed my mind,
l've changed my mind

1148
01:23:37,840 --> 01:23:40,900
Yeah,
l've changed my mind, oh...

1149
01:23:56,758 --> 01:23:58,885
Come on... come on.

1150
01:23:58,961 --> 01:24:03,591
lt doesn't like
to move the large numbers.

1151
01:24:03,665 --> 01:24:05,724
Did you ever think you'd be up
this late

1152
01:24:05,801 --> 01:24:07,393
restructuring a media company?

1153
01:24:07,469 --> 01:24:09,596
l thought l was going
to be a rock star.

1154
01:25:37,859 --> 01:25:39,292
l won't make stupid threats

1155
01:25:39,361 --> 01:25:41,829
but you're not going
to run away with this guy

1156
01:25:41,897 --> 01:25:45,333
because wherever you go,
l can follow you...

1157
01:25:45,400 --> 01:25:48,392
even if it's to the woods
in New Hampshire.

1158
01:25:53,742 --> 01:25:56,939
Why don't you yell?

1159
01:25:57,045 --> 01:25:58,672
Come on, l dare you.

1160
01:26:17,599 --> 01:26:19,157
Hey, hey, are you okay?

1161
01:26:19,234 --> 01:26:21,634
What's the matter?

1162
01:26:21,703 --> 01:26:23,034
Let's just leave.

1163
01:26:23,105 --> 01:26:24,094
What happened?

1164
01:26:27,476 --> 01:26:29,842
He was here.

1165
01:26:29,911 --> 01:26:31,310
Who? Embry?

1166
01:26:31,380 --> 01:26:32,711
Well, where is he?

1167
01:26:32,781 --> 01:26:33,839
Where'd he go?

1168
01:26:35,417 --> 01:26:37,851
l'll take care
of this right now.

1169
01:26:37,919 --> 01:26:41,855
No, don't.
That's what he wants.

1170
01:26:41,923 --> 01:26:43,413
He'll hurt you.

1171
01:26:45,394 --> 01:26:47,123
Just wait here.

1172
01:27:05,047 --> 01:27:06,674
Why don't you join us?

1173
01:27:11,119 --> 01:27:12,586
You're going to be great.

1174
01:27:24,633 --> 01:27:26,533
You shouldn't be in here.

1175
01:27:26,601 --> 01:27:29,593
l'm coming with you.

1176
01:27:29,671 --> 01:27:32,003
Well, where do you think he is?

1177
01:27:32,074 --> 01:27:33,166
He's right there.

1178
01:27:35,277 --> 01:27:38,735
Hey.

1179
01:27:38,814 --> 01:27:39,906
Embry, stop!

1180
01:27:39,981 --> 01:27:42,415
l want to talk to you!

1181
01:27:56,631 --> 01:27:58,622
Hey, Embry?

1182
01:28:13,215 --> 01:28:14,239
Hey, Embry?

1183
01:28:17,052 --> 01:28:18,747
Come on out.

1184
01:28:18,820 --> 01:28:19,787
l'm a police officer.

1185
01:28:19,855 --> 01:28:20,981
l've got a gun.

1186
01:28:21,056 --> 01:28:23,183
l don't want to hurt you.

1187
01:28:38,039 --> 01:28:39,438
Embry?

1188
01:28:42,010 --> 01:28:44,672
Hey.

1189
01:28:44,746 --> 01:28:47,579
l heard what you said up there.

1190
01:28:47,649 --> 01:28:48,843
lt was amazing.

1191
01:28:48,917 --> 01:28:51,647
lt was
an incredible performance.

1192
01:28:51,720 --> 01:28:54,746
l wasn't... acting.

1193
01:28:54,823 --> 01:28:57,951
But we're... leaving together.

1194
01:29:04,533 --> 01:29:07,400
Stick with finance, Katie.

1195
01:29:07,469 --> 01:29:08,936
lt's what you're good at.

1196
01:29:10,872 --> 01:29:11,930
Embry!

1197
01:29:19,247 --> 01:29:20,305
Embry!

1198
01:29:23,785 --> 01:29:25,252
Embry, wait!

1199
01:29:26,855 --> 01:29:28,652
We're leaving together.

1200
01:29:28,723 --> 01:29:30,520
You think l'd take you
to Europe?

1201
01:29:30,592 --> 01:29:32,423
You'd just stand around
awkwardly

1202
01:29:32,494 --> 01:29:34,052
and l'd feel sorry for you.

1203
01:29:34,129 --> 01:29:36,495
l love you!

1204
01:29:36,565 --> 01:29:38,294
Really?

1205
01:29:38,366 --> 01:29:40,834
We made love right over there.

1206
01:29:40,902 --> 01:29:43,837
And now l can't get away
from you fast enough.

1207
01:29:43,905 --> 01:29:44,929
Embry!

1208
01:29:47,209 --> 01:29:48,699
Look at you.

1209
01:29:48,777 --> 01:29:51,177
You have no grace.

1210
01:29:51,246 --> 01:29:52,178
What are you doing?!

1211
01:29:52,247 --> 01:29:55,239
Crazy bitch.

1212
01:29:55,317 --> 01:29:57,251
You can't come with me.

1213
01:30:00,388 --> 01:30:01,582
Embry, why are you doing this?!

1214
01:30:01,656 --> 01:30:04,625
Look at me!

1215
01:30:04,693 --> 01:30:05,751
Embry!

1216
01:30:05,827 --> 01:30:07,556
Katie!

1217
01:30:09,331 --> 01:30:11,731
There's no one there.

1218
01:30:11,800 --> 01:30:15,031
There's no one.

1219
01:30:15,103 --> 01:30:16,934
No one.

1220
01:30:25,847 --> 01:30:28,179
We're not going away together,
are we?

1221
01:30:28,250 --> 01:30:31,617
We're not going to New Hampshire
together, are we?

1222
01:30:31,686 --> 01:30:32,812
We'll get you help, okay?

1223
01:30:32,887 --> 01:30:34,149
-No. Listen.
-l want to come.

1224
01:30:34,222 --> 01:30:35,211
l want to go with you.

1225
01:30:35,290 --> 01:30:36,222
You'll be okay.

1226
01:30:36,291 --> 01:30:37,724
l want to go with you.

1227
01:30:37,792 --> 01:30:39,521
