Look.

1229
01:32:12,887 --> 01:32:15,617
That's pretty.

1230
01:32:15,690 --> 01:32:19,023
There's snow on the roofs.

1231
01:32:22,530 --> 01:32:25,021
Katie, listen.

1232
01:32:27,635 --> 01:32:30,331
