to making partner.

1233
01:32:33,308 --> 01:32:37,039
We both know the rules
about interoffice romance.

1234
01:32:37,112 --> 01:32:39,945
l wish we could keep seeing
each other

1235
01:32:40,081 --> 01:32:43,539
but it's just not worth
the risk.

1236
01:32:43,618 --> 01:32:46,086
